# MULTIPLE FORMATS
# ====================

# Inline format
[Quick Settings: Volume: 0-100, Mute: no, Save or Cancel]

# Natural confirmation
confirm "Delete all data?" with Yes or No

# Structured with sections
Advanced Settings:
  --- Audio ---
  Master: 0-100 = 80
  Effects: 0-100 = 50
  Music: 0-100 = 70
  
  --- Video ---
  Resolution: 720p | 1080p | 4K
  Frame Rate: 30 | 60 | 120 | 144
  VSync: on
  
  --- Performance ---
  when Resolution = 4K:
    ! High resolution may impact performance
    DLSS: Off | Quality | Performance
    
  when Frame Rate > 60:
    ? Requires high-end GPU
    Adaptive Sync: yes
  
  ---
  Apply | Reset | Cancel

